Interface Summary
IJoinCondition Defines all join condition methods.
IOrderCondition Defines all order condition methods.
ISqlGenerator SQL element capable of generating SQL text.
IValueCondition Defines all value condition methods.

DataObjectBinding Defines binding information for a data object.
DbUtil Utility class providing database related services for opening connections, closing connections, committing and rolling back transactions, closing SQL statements and result sets, retrieving data as different data types from a SQL result set and setting SQL parameters of different data types in a prepared SQL statement.

JoinConditions Class representing multiple SQL join conditions.

Operators Static class representing SQL condition operators.
OrderCondition Class representing a SQL order condition using bound data object information.
OrderConditions Class representing multiple SQL order conditions.
ValueCondition Class representing a SQL value condition using bound data object information.
ValueConditions Class representing multiple SQL value conditions.
